{"tid":1466548,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家記緊2015年光復行動教訓，請勿割席","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:20.000Z","uid":88713,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"783556ac1614f839e7ef8ae857f5ac1cc87ae90b","tid":1466548,"uid":88713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:52.000Z","msg":"這是運動第二個輿論關口。第一次是七一衝擊立法會，大家僥倖渡過了，沒有割席事件。<br />\n<br />\n今次是第二次。隨著運動的深入，愈多愈多不同的人會受牽連，阻人登機、圍堵敵軍，可能某程度走得太前，予公眾觀感未必好，部分行動有改善空間。但如果香港人連這一步都跨不過，運動註定一事無成。<br />\n<br />\n2015年光復行動，前線捉住一對青關會母女，細路女大喊，泛民割席譴責，本土泛民自此勢成水火。歷史的教訓，大家還記得嗎？<br />\n<br />\n敵人無底線，我們不一定要跟著他們無底線。但當有隊友可能走得太前時，我們要做的是支援他們。可以檢討，可以提改善建議，但that's all，請勿割席，拒絕任何負面的指摘。<br />\n<br />\n記住，激進化的雞蛋，仍是雞蛋。"},{"pid":"a3479e8cd21b202c4921dde4d40a0b24da44c66c","tid":1466548,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58bcc837f634bf2ca72e957f15b9a8a92d648b2","tid":1466548,"uid":88713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"推推先"},{"pid":"05a5846d51c66b2df836c100d158680a1a13633e","tid":1466548,"uid":235374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:34.000Z","msg":"今日有兩個重要信息 <br />\n一係要拆鬼呢招 對家玩spy防不勝防 要想辦法破狗狗情報網/截取狗狗情報<br />\n二係前線手足呢兩個月壓力好大 情緒控制唔好 可能要休養下 和理非要出場<br />\n<br />\n其實今日好小事 與721 811相比 雞毛蒜皮<br />\n文宣 要拆今日單野 盡量冷處理"},{"pid":"24ae625443c01d9aeaddb781fdcf36d86a5f5362","tid":1466548,"uid":88713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:47.000Z","msg":"和理非要做嘅首要任務，係接力救輿論，而非掉轉頭指摘，否則運動不攻自破"},{"pid":"4db8dcb894fa41ca35e9c2879e8289897cd32923","tid":1466548,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>聽日一定要做！！！！<br />\n<br />\n理撚得佢有冇鬼！！！！<br />\n<br />\n讓條路俾旅客，然後禮貌鞠躬道歉！！！！<br />\n<br />\n今晚大家早d翻去，準備文宣！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"75eb30a073fdfc7de9c810355792b73c01e2cff3","tid":1466548,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367cb5ce941483d09bdd6e1224bd05b77ded0307","tid":1466548,"uid":88713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e0c0cefecf9b1eabf2e5e954e5a61f5be834954","tid":1466548,"uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:56.000Z","msg":"係室飽機場    係包和機場   唔係佔領機場      唔係癱瘓機場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466104</a>"},{"pid":"92865ee120c766ff03283ae496a2660c724b6fd9","tid":1466548,"uid":88713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6105c4f02a08f84286f21c71d3368128945ab81b","tid":1466548,"uid":88713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:48.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"a1f3c19e18f98fb4711e47c8ae793808ceece5f8","tid":1466548,"uid":88713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6492a782b9f6cec461338a2be586cd67ab40e1e1","tid":1466548,"uid":88713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:20.000Z","msg":"再退一步講，即使今次行動真係失左一定程度民意，但抗爭者士氣，點都重要過外面唔關事班人點諗，that's the main point。<br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解警察可以打人唔使本呀？因為佢做到幾賤，班大嘅都攬佢哋呀嘛，咁佢哋梗係冇後顧之憂啦<br />\n<br />\n唔係話民意完全唔重要，但而家係埋牙肉搏，當你連班抗爭核心都得罪埋，空有民意又有何用"}]}